data.description: SELLER OFFERING BUYER, AT CLOSING, $5,000 TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS. This 3-bedroom 2-ba home features hardwood floors in foyer, living room, dining room and hallway. Carpet in bedrooms and bonus room. Tile in kitchen/nook and bathrooms. French doors lead from living room to dining room/office. Living room has a corner fireplace. Deck is accessed via living room & is great for outside dining and/or relaxing. Hall bath has single vanity and tub. Master bath has double vanity, garden tub and separate shower.
